packages.title: Fun-Filled Munnar Thekkady Tour
packages.description: Travelling with your partner means hoping for a travel destination that offers you the perfect romantic ambiance. Mountains, serenity, and peace are what youre craving, and in that case, Kerala is the ideal spot to explore. Check out our Munnar Thekkady honeymoon tour package.

itinerary.title: Arrive in Cochin - Munnar
itinerary.details: Upon your arrival in Cochin, our tour representatives will greet you and take you to Munnar. Visit the Athirapilly Falls on the way. Check-in to your hotel and relax for a while before heading out to explore Munnar.

itinerary.title: Munnar Sightseeing
itinerary.details: Explore the scenic tea gardens of Munnar, visit Mattupetty Dam, Echo Point, and the Tea Museum. Enjoy the breathtaking views of the misty hills.

itinerary.title: Munnar to Thekkady
itinerary.details: After breakfast, check out from your hotel and proceed to Thekkady. Visit the Periyar Wildlife Sanctuary and enjoy a boat ride on Periyar Lake.

itinerary.title: Thekkady - Alleppey
itinerary.details: Check out from your hotel in Thekkady and proceed to Alleppey. Enjoy a serene houseboat cruise through the backwaters of Kerala.

itinerary.title: Departure from Cochin
itinerary.details: After breakfast, check out from the houseboat and proceed to Cochin for your return journey.

packages.title: Nilgiris: The Blue Mountains
packages.description: Discover serene landscapes, lush tea gardens, and cool, misty heights in The Nilgiris. Enjoy the tranquility and natural beauty of this picturesque destination.

itinerary.title: Arrival in Coimbatore - The Nilgiris
itinerary.details: Upon your arrival in Coimbatore, our tour representatives will greet you and take you to The Nilgiris. Check-in to your hotel and relax for a while before exploring the local surroundings.

itinerary.title: Exploring The Nilgiris
itinerary.details: Visit the botanical gardens, enjoy a ride on the Nilgiri Mountain Railway, and explore the picturesque tea estates of The Nilgiris.

itinerary.title: Coonoor Sightseeing
itinerary.details: Proceed to Coonoor, visit Sim's Park, Lamb's Rock, and Dolphin's Nose viewpoint. Experience the serene beauty of these attractions.

itinerary.title: Departure from Coimbatore
itinerary.details: After breakfast, check out from your hotel and proceed to Coimbatore for your return journey.

packages.title: Delhi, Agra, Jaipur: Experience the essence of India's rich history and vibrant culture!
packages.description: Explore the rich history and vibrant culture of India through its iconic cities!

itinerary.title: Arrival in Delhi
itinerary.details: Arrive in Delhi and check in to your hotel. Explore local markets in the evening.

itinerary.title: Delhi Sightseeing
itinerary.details: Visit historical sites like India Gate, Qutub Minar, and Red Fort.

itinerary.title: Delhi to Agra
itinerary.details: Drive to Agra. Visit the magnificent Taj Mahal and Agra Fort.

itinerary.title: Agra to Jaipur
itinerary.details: Proceed to Jaipur. Visit Fatehpur Sikri en route.

itinerary.title: Jaipur Exploration
itinerary.details: Explore Amber Fort, City Palace, and Hawa Mahal.

itinerary.title: Jaipur to Delhi
itinerary.details: Return to Delhi for last-minute shopping and exploration.

itinerary.title: Departure
itinerary.details: Transfer to the airport for your onward journey.

packages.title: Rajasthan Royalty
packages.description: Embrace the regal charm of magnificent palaces, historic forts, and desert landscapes!

itinerary.title: Arrival in Jaipur
itinerary.details: Welcome to the Pink City! Check-in to your hotel and relax.

itinerary.title: Jaipur Sightseeing
itinerary.details: Visit the Amber Fort, City Palace, and Hawa Mahal.

itinerary.title: Jaipur to Jodhpur
itinerary.details: Drive to Jodhpur. Explore Mehrangarh Fort and the Blue City.

itinerary.title: Jodhpur to Udaipur
itinerary.details: Travel to Udaipur, known for its beautiful lakes. Enjoy a boat ride on Lake Pichola.

itinerary.title: Udaipur Exploration
itinerary.details: Visit the City Palace, Jag Mandir, and Saheliyon-ki-Bari.

itinerary.title: Udaipur to Pushkar
itinerary.details: Proceed to Pushkar and visit the famous Brahma Temple.

itinerary.title: Pushkar to Jaipur
itinerary.details: Return to Jaipur and relax at leisure.

itinerary.title: Departure
itinerary.details: Transfer to the airport for your onward journey.

packages.title: Goa Getaway
packages.description: Relax on sun-kissed beaches, enjoy vibrant nightlife, and savor delicious seafood!

itinerary.title: Arrival in Goa
itinerary.details: Check-in to your hotel and relax. Explore nearby beaches.

itinerary.title: North Goa Sightseeing
itinerary.details: Visit Fort Aguada, Anjuna Beach, and enjoy the local market.

itinerary.title: South Goa Exploration
itinerary.details: Explore Palolem Beach, Cabo de Rama Fort, and relax.

itinerary.title: Leisure Day
itinerary.details: Enjoy a day at leisure, indulge in water sports or relax on the beach.

itinerary.title: Departure
itinerary.details: Transfer to the airport for your return journey.

packages.title: Himalayan Retreat
packages.description: Discover breathtaking mountain vistas, serene monasteries, and invigorating treks!

itinerary.title: Arrival in Dharamshala
itinerary.details: Check-in to your hotel and explore local markets.

itinerary.title: Dharamshala Sightseeing
itinerary.details: Visit Tsuglagkhang Complex, Bhagsu Waterfall, and explore McLeod Ganj.

itinerary.title: Trekking in Triund
itinerary.details: Trek to Triund and enjoy breathtaking views of the Dhauladhar range.

itinerary.title: Visit to Palampur
itinerary.details: Explore tea gardens and enjoy a local lunch.

itinerary.title: Return to Dharamshala
itinerary.details: Leisure day in Dharamshala.

itinerary.title: Departure
itinerary.details: Transfer to the airport for your return journey.
